id: pm-4a1p
title: "GH-249: create --status closed bypasses governance.require_close_reason"
description: "pm create <type> <title> --status closed records NO close_reason and emits NO warning under governance.require_close_reason, unlike pm close (errors) and pm update --status closed (defaults + warns). Mirror update: derive close_reason from --message/--resolution else default placeholder, write it, emit close_reason_defaulted warning."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[3]: create,governance,validation
