author: claude-code-agent
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: Derive close_reason from --message/--resolution else placeholder; emit close_reason_defaulted.
expected_result: Closed-at-create honors require_close_reason like the other closure paths
actual_result: Implemented in create.ts; covered by 4 new create tests.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-16T15:25:59.891Z",claude-code-agent,"GH-249 fix: pm create --status closed now honors governance.require_close_reason. When status resolves to the close_status and require_close_reason is enabled, create derives close_reason from --message > --resolution else the CREATE_DIRECT_CLOSE_REASON_DEFAULT placeholder, writes it to front-matter, and pushes a close_reason_defaulted warning when defaulted — mirroring pm update --status closed. Files: cli/commands/create.ts, core/shared/constants.ts."
close_reason: "create --status closed now records a close_reason and warns under governance.require_close_reason, matching pm close and pm update."
